    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1925-01-24T21:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1925-01-24T21:00:00-05:00" n="261"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d261">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">815.00/3535: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dennis</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tegucigalpa</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-01-24T20:00:00-06:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 24, 1925—8 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 25—12:36 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>13. Please instruct with regard to my participation in the inaugural ceremonies
                    February 1st and as to form of extending recognition to the new constitutional
                    government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dennis</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
